videos.description: Jaylen Brown gets the steal and throws it up to Javonte Green who impressively throws it down with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brown goes up top to Green for impressive alley-oop) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown goes up top to Green for impressive alley-oop

videos.description: Seth Curry comes off a ball screen and throws a slick, behind-the-back pass to Joel Embiid, who cans a midrange jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry goes behind the back to Embiid for the jumper) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry goes behind the back to Embiid for the jumper

videos.description: Tacko Fall bats the offensive rebound to himself and puts in the follow slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tacko barely gets off the ground for putback dunk) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tacko barely gets off the ground for putback dunk

videos.description: Shake Milton looks to get accustomed to his new teammate as he throws the lob to Dwight Howard who stuffs it home with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Milton throws the lob to Howard for the jam) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton throws the lob to Howard for the jam

videos.description: Jaylen Brown drives down the lane and goes for a huge slam on Joel Embiid, but it clanks off the rim.
videos.headline: Brown nearly posterizes Embiid

videos.description: Marcus Smart dives on the floor for the loose ball and tosses it up to Javonte Green who crams home the monster dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart’s hustle leads to huge Green dunk) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smart's hustle leads to huge Green dunk

videos.description: Ben Simmons attacks his defender with a series of handles and finishes with his off hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons shows off handles for sweet reverse) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons shows off handles for sweet reverse

videos.description: Tacko Fall gathers himself after catching the pass and puts in the floater.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tacko calmly puts in the floater) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tacko calmly puts in the floater

videos.description: Jayson Tatum scores 10 points and dishes out a couple assists as he makes his preseason debut.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Tatum goes for 10 in preseason debut) 2020/12/15 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Tatum goes for 10 in preseason debut

videos.description: Joel Embiid goes for 18, while Ben Simmons scores 10 and hands out six assists as the 76ers take down the Celtics in both teams' first preseason game.
